      <title>铁矿石价格跌至五周低点，因交易商担心中国需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/iron-ore-hits-five-week-low-as-traders-fret-about-chinese-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国工业利润不佳凸显了该国经济的疲软，尽管钢厂的业绩确实有所改善，但铁矿石价格仍跌至五周多以来的最低水平，跌破每吨 100 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/iron-ore-hits-five-week-low-as-traders-fret-about-chinese-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 02:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
